title: 11/05/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 11/05/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses the effects that COVID will have on tonight's matchup between the Niners and Packers. Would they be playing this game if Aaron Rodgers was out due to the Virus? We're joined by NFL Network inside Ian Rapaport and NBCS Sports Bay Area 49ers Insider, Matt Maiocco.
